- **Implementation:** Created `/adapt/platform/novaops/nova_framework/scripts/bridge_monitor.py` as persistent service
- **Impact:** Production-ready, maintainable monitoring solution; verified end-to-end functionality
- **Result:** Bridge Monitor operational (PID 619618) and successfully receiving messages
- **Validation:** Quality over speed philosophy proven correct again (15-minute fix vs fragile hack)

